ReadMe

Drill ID: JD_2026_06_W4_StudyLogManager

Class Name: StudyLogManager

Difficulty: Level 2 — Multi-Class Application

Estimated Time: 45–60 minutes

Actual Time Taken: 47 minutes

Written by: Chanwoo Park

Problem
Create a console-based Study Log Manager that allows the user to add study logs,
view all logs, calculate total study time, and save logs to a file.

Program Flow
The main method creates a Scanner and a StudyLogService. It repeatedly shows a menu,
receives user input, creates StudyLog objects, and calls StudyLogService methods.

Class Responsibilities
StudyLogMain controls the console menu and user input.
StudyLog stores one study session.
StudyLogService manages multiple logs, calculations, and file saving.

Object Collaboration
StudyLogMain creates StudyLog objects and passes them to StudyLogService.
StudyLogService stores and processes those objects.